[101 Marriages]

18
00:01:44,430 --> 00:01:47,430
[Episode 7]

19
00:01:54,910 --> 00:01:57,160
Han Chengchi texted me

20
00:01:57,660 --> 00:02:00,000
about going to the lake next week.

21
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:01,160
You agreed?

22
00:02:04,250 --> 00:02:06,870
I love watching the drama.

23
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,950
Are you wearing these
for your wedding photos?

24
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,790
Let me see.

25
00:02:32,370 --> 00:02:33,000
Chengchi recreated

26
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,790
the baby outfits from when

27
00:02:34,950 --> 00:02:36,160
we first met.

28
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,700
He's such a romantic.

29
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,500
Standing around is boring.

30
00:02:46,660 --> 00:02:48,120
Let's gossip.

31
00:02:48,450 --> 00:02:50,410
I know a secret about Lanshan.

32
00:02:50,620 --> 00:02:51,700
Want to hear it?

33
00:02:51,950 --> 00:02:53,120
Nope.

34
00:02:53,540 --> 00:02:54,750
If I wanted to know,

35
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:55,910
I'd just read my fortune.

36
00:02:56,450 --> 00:02:57,410
So, zip it.

37
00:02:58,910 --> 00:02:59,910
Good call.

38
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:05,700
Lanshan was a magnet for guys

39
00:03:05,830 --> 00:03:07,450
in high school.

40
00:03:07,830 --> 00:03:09,580
Tons of them tried to win her over,

41
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:11,250
but she didn't
give any of them a chance.

42
00:03:11,410 --> 00:03:13,200
Ever wonder why?

43
00:03:16,910 --> 00:03:18,750
Turns out, the guy she liked

44
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:20,410
was right here.

45
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:22,450
And that person is...

46
00:03:22,580 --> 00:03:23,500
Jiayi,

47
00:03:23,790 --> 00:03:25,330
everyone knew

48
00:03:25,410 --> 00:03:27,000
Lanshan was into Shwenny,

49
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:27,910
so

50
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,290
there's no surprise there.

51
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:31,200
Nope, you're off.

52
00:03:31,370 --> 00:03:33,160
Back then, she wasn't into Shi.

53
00:03:33,410 --> 00:03:34,120
I mean,

54
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,540
if she was,

55
00:03:35,620 --> 00:03:37,500
why did she run away from the wedding?

56
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:38,790
So you're saying

57
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:41,000
she didn't like me but you do?

58
00:03:41,660 --> 00:03:42,330
That flirty text

59
00:03:42,370 --> 00:03:43,410
last night...

60
00:03:43,540 --> 00:03:44,540
Was that your way

61
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:45,790
of confessing?

62
00:03:48,660 --> 00:03:49,950
So, Miss Wang, all this talk

63
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,160
was about my husband?

64
00:03:51,410 --> 00:03:53,540
Didn't realize you cared so much.

65
00:03:53,620 --> 00:03:54,500
Shi,

66
00:03:54,620 --> 00:03:56,250
why are you always defending her?

67
00:03:56,370 --> 00:03:57,410
If you hadn't paid

68
00:03:57,540 --> 00:03:58,160
for her brother's treatment,

69
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,040
would she have married you?

70
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,120
It doesn't matter

71
00:04:00,250 --> 00:04:01,660
why I married Sheng Shi.

72
00:04:01,750 --> 00:04:03,160
That's between us.

73
00:04:03,250 --> 00:04:04,120
Just know this:

74
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,290
he's my husband,

75
00:04:05,540 --> 00:04:06,790
which makes him

76
00:04:07,500 --> 00:04:08,660
mine.

77
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:10,200
I don't care

78
00:04:10,290 --> 00:04:11,450
how much you like him,

79
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:13,000
but as long as we're married,

80
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:15,120
hands off.

81
00:04:15,620 --> 00:04:17,370
If I catch you

82
00:04:17,450 --> 00:04:18,660
messaging him again,

83
00:04:18,910 --> 00:04:20,040
or hear

84
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:21,660
about you crossing the line,

85
00:04:21,910 --> 00:04:23,330
don't blame me for what happens.

86
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,330
Putting a mistress in her place
is only right.

87
00:04:26,450 --> 00:04:27,790
Do you all agree?

88
00:04:27,950 --> 00:04:28,950
Absolutely.

89
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:32,160
Besides,
she doesn't even count as a mistress.

90
00:04:32,450 --> 00:04:33,410
Gu Lanshan,

91
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:34,790
you think I don't know

92
00:04:34,910 --> 00:04:36,040
your dirty secrets?

93
00:04:36,290 --> 00:04:37,950
Today, I'm spilling

94
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:38,790
who you really liked back then...

95
00:04:38,910 --> 00:04:39,750
Jiayi!

96
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,120
Get over here!

97
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:05,290
Auntie, why'd you stop me?

98
00:05:05,450 --> 00:05:06,540
That sneaky witch has always

99
00:05:06,660 --> 00:05:07,700
had a thing for Chengchi.

100
00:05:07,910 --> 00:05:09,330
If I expose her now,

101
00:05:09,370 --> 00:05:10,370
Shi won't have any reason

102
00:05:10,450 --> 00:05:11,580
to protect her.

103
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:12,950
If you say anything,

104
00:05:13,290 --> 00:05:15,120
don't ever call me Auntie again.

105
00:05:15,330 --> 00:05:16,250
Come on, Auntie,

106
00:05:16,330 --> 00:05:17,000
I was just trying to

107
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:19,000
help you deal with Lanshan.

108
00:05:19,330 --> 00:05:20,660
Don't be mad.

109
00:05:20,950 --> 00:05:21,790
Tell me,

110
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,660
how'd you even find out?

111
00:05:23,910 --> 00:05:25,080
A while back,

112
00:05:25,290 --> 00:05:26,950
when Lanshan was sick,

113
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:29,160
I went to her place with En
and Chengchi.

114
00:05:31,450 --> 00:05:33,120
I stumbled on

115
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,450
this photo.

116
00:05:36,140 --> 00:05:38,470
[Your name, my secret]

117
00:05:41,950 --> 00:05:43,790
Forget you ever knew

118
00:05:43,950 --> 00:05:45,200
about Lanshan

119
00:05:46,250 --> 00:05:47,500
liking Chengchi.

120
00:05:47,910 --> 00:05:49,000
Why?

121
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:51,500
Why are you protecting her, too?

122
00:05:52,370 --> 00:05:53,040
Chengchi and En

123
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,870
are finally getting married.

124
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:56,290
I won't let anything

125
00:05:56,410 --> 00:05:58,000
mess that up.

126
00:06:00,250 --> 00:06:01,660
Don't bring it up

127
00:06:01,790 --> 00:06:02,870
again,

128
00:06:03,370 --> 00:06:04,580
or I'm done

129
00:06:04,700 --> 00:06:05,910
with you.

130
00:06:07,290 --> 00:06:08,200
Alright, I get it.

131
00:06:08,660 --> 00:06:10,000
Give me the photo.

132
00:06:11,750 --> 00:06:12,540
And remember,

133
00:06:13,370 --> 00:06:15,040
there's nothing

134
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,450
between Lanshan and Chengchi.

135
00:06:17,950 --> 00:06:18,870
Fine.

136
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,870
I'll send you both a gift.

137
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:30,910
You said I'm yours. Was that for real?

138
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:32,950
No.

139
00:06:38,540 --> 00:06:39,160
Now,

140
00:06:39,290 --> 00:06:40,160
apologize.

141
00:06:41,250 --> 00:06:42,250
I'm sorry.

142
00:06:43,410 --> 00:06:45,450
What? I can't hear.

143
00:06:45,950 --> 00:06:47,080
Sorry!

144
00:06:48,910 --> 00:06:50,330
Oh.

145
00:06:50,580 --> 00:06:51,950
You're sorry for what?

146
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:00,250
All done with your makeup?

147
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,410
Do I look pretty?

148
00:07:04,250 --> 00:07:06,410
You're the prettiest woman in the world.

149
00:07:13,330 --> 00:07:14,040
We need to

150
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:15,540
crack down

151
00:07:15,660 --> 00:07:17,080
on shady traders

152
00:07:17,290 --> 00:07:18,370
and clean up

153
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:20,540
the stock market.

154
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:26,870
Your bags are packed.

155
00:07:26,950 --> 00:07:28,620
You've got a flight tomorrow.
Get some rest.

156
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:29,410
Okay.

157
00:07:44,290 --> 00:07:45,700
Are you free next Wednesday?

158
00:07:45,910 --> 00:07:46,910
Wednesday?

159
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,910
Not sure.

160
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:48,950
Why?

161
00:07:49,660 --> 00:07:51,290
Come home early.

162
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:54,330
Wednesday...

163
00:07:54,910 --> 00:07:56,160
It's Sheng Shi's birthday.

164
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,120
Alright.

165
00:08:18,790 --> 00:08:20,540
Blue makes him look tanned.

166
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:23,700
His face is already dark enough.

167
00:08:31,370 --> 00:08:32,620
This one's nice,

168
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:36,120
but maybe too red.

169
00:08:40,910 --> 00:08:42,750
It's so hard to pick a gift.

170
00:08:43,040 --> 00:08:44,790
If he hadn't given me that card,

171
00:08:44,910 --> 00:08:45,870
I really...

172
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,580
Excuse me.

173
00:08:55,750 --> 00:08:56,250
Hello.

174
00:08:56,370 --> 00:08:58,120
Can you wrap this tie for me?

175
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:58,540
Of course.

176
00:08:58,660 --> 00:09:00,000
Great choice.

177
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:02,250
This is our newest limited edition.

178
00:09:02,370 --> 00:09:03,790
Perfect for your husband.

179
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:04,750
Could you

180
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:06,250
add a card, too?

181
00:09:06,330 --> 00:09:07,370
Sure, just a moment.

182
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:17,160
Here you go.

183
00:09:17,250 --> 00:09:18,290
Thanks a lot.

184
00:09:27,290 --> 00:09:28,120
Excuse me,

185
00:09:28,250 --> 00:09:28,910
what did

186
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,700
the lady buy?

187
00:09:30,830 --> 00:09:32,080
A limited edition tie.

188
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:33,660
Only six are available across the country.

189
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:35,870
Really?

190
00:09:35,910 --> 00:09:37,080
I'll take one, too.

191
00:09:37,370 --> 00:09:38,120
Sure.

192
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,910
Lanshan, breakfast's ready.

193
00:09:57,450 --> 00:09:58,950
When was this taken?

194
00:09:59,910 --> 00:10:01,040
So sweet.

195
00:10:02,250 --> 00:10:04,160
Mr. Sheng might be back today.

196
00:10:04,370 --> 00:10:05,410
I know.

197
00:10:14,470 --> 00:10:15,810
[Got a room at FUN tonight.
Want me to pick you up?]

198
00:10:15,810 --> 00:10:18,140
[I have a meeting.
I'll head over after.]

199
00:10:23,910 --> 00:10:25,250
Hello, your delivery.

200
00:10:25,410 --> 00:10:26,080
Is it for me?

201
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:26,910
Yes.

202
00:10:27,290 --> 00:10:27,870
Thanks.

203
00:10:27,950 --> 00:10:28,750
You're welcome.

204
00:10:31,430 --> 00:10:33,520
[Chengchi: Happy birthday!
Love, Miss Gu]

205
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:36,120
"Love, Miss Gu."

206
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:47,450
Forget you ever knew

207
