about Lanshan

208
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:51,120
liking Chengchi.

209
00:10:51,250 --> 00:10:52,330
Why?

210
00:10:52,950 --> 00:10:54,910
Why are you protecting her, too?

211
00:10:55,040 --> 00:10:55,620
Chengchi and En

212
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:57,290
are finally getting married.

213
00:10:57,450 --> 00:10:58,660
I won't let anything

214
00:10:58,830 --> 00:11:00,250
mess that up.

215
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:03,790
Lanshan and Chengchi? Not happening,

216
00:11:04,410 --> 00:11:05,330
so let it go.

217
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:08,000
Chengchi's birthday is coming up.

218
00:11:08,290 --> 00:11:10,330
He's going to love this gift.

219
00:11:15,450 --> 00:11:17,080
I made this bracelet myself.

220
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,450
It might not be the prettiest,

221
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:20,000
but it matches mine.

222
00:11:22,700 --> 00:11:23,500
En,

223
00:11:23,660 --> 00:11:24,750
what are you up to?

224
00:11:25,250 --> 00:11:26,790
When did you get here, Chengchi?

225
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:27,870
What are you doing?

226
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,160
Why so mysterious?

227
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:30,700
Nothing.

228
00:11:30,830 --> 00:11:33,120
Come on, let's not keep them waiting.

229
00:11:33,250 --> 00:11:33,790
Okay.

230
00:11:33,950 --> 00:11:34,660
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

231
00:11:47,250 --> 00:11:48,620
Finally done.

232
00:11:59,310 --> 00:12:01,220
[Unknown Caller]

233
00:12:04,940 --> 00:12:05,400
Hello?

234
00:12:06,410 --> 00:12:08,160
Is this Miss Gu Lanshan?

235
00:12:08,910 --> 00:12:11,160
Yes, who's this?

236
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:13,330
I'm calling from the hospital.

237
00:12:15,370 --> 00:12:16,950
What happened to my brother?

238
00:12:17,700 --> 00:12:19,040
Miss Gu, don't worry.

239
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:20,620
Mr. Ye Mo just woke up,

240
00:12:20,660 --> 00:12:22,660
and the doctors are checking on him.

241
00:12:22,830 --> 00:12:23,910
Can you come

242
00:12:23,950 --> 00:12:24,950
to the hospital?

243
00:12:25,040 --> 00:12:26,330
Yes.

244
00:12:26,450 --> 00:12:27,750
I'll be there right away.

245
00:12:29,640 --> 00:12:31,470
[Inpatient]

246
00:12:39,450 --> 00:12:41,410
Doctor, how is my brother?

247
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:42,580
His internal injuries

248
00:12:42,660 --> 00:12:44,500
aren't too serious.

249
00:12:45,410 --> 00:12:46,200
With some time and care,

250
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:47,500
he should recover about 70-80%.

251
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:48,830
His legs, though, are weak

252
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:50,370
from being immobile for so long.

253
00:12:50,750 --> 00:12:52,450
But with therapy,

254
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:55,040
he'll be back on his feet eventually.

255
00:12:55,660 --> 00:12:56,660
Thank you, Doctor.

256
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:57,750
You can probably

257
00:12:57,910 --> 00:12:59,250
see him soon.

258
00:12:59,450 --> 00:13:00,950
Thank you.

259
00:13:01,040 --> 00:13:03,040
No problem.

260
00:13:03,450 --> 00:13:05,450
Keep an eye on him
and record any changes.

261
00:13:10,950 --> 00:13:11,790
Chu.

262
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:14,790
Mo,

263
00:13:15,450 --> 00:13:17,040
you're finally awake.

264
00:13:17,660 --> 00:13:19,040
Are you free now?

265
00:13:21,660 --> 00:13:22,620
Tell me,

266
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:25,290
did we succeed?

267
00:13:27,620 --> 00:13:29,410
I married Sheng Shi.

268
00:13:30,500 --> 00:13:31,290
Chu,

269
00:13:33,580 --> 00:13:34,910
are you happy

270
00:13:35,790 --> 00:13:36,950
with him?

271
00:13:38,790 --> 00:13:39,660
I...

272
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:42,330
We are

273
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:44,290
doing well.

274
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:46,040
Things are much better now.

275
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:47,870
Don't worry.

276
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:23,120
♪Summer breeze♪

277
00:14:23,830 --> 00:14:27,500
♪Deep blue skies♪

278
00:14:28,580 --> 00:14:31,910
♪Dear, it's you♪

279
00:14:33,410 --> 00:14:35,040
♪In golden light♪

280
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:38,160
Nice tie, Chengchi.

281
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:39,500
Thanks.

282
00:14:39,830 --> 00:14:40,790
This tie

283
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:43,040
is my favorite!

284
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:46,580
♪Blowing on my face♪

285
00:14:47,830 --> 00:14:51,580
♪Summer's warm embrace♪

286
00:14:52,660 --> 00:14:56,910
♪Love in the air♪

287
00:14:57,700 --> 00:14:59,660
Where are you going?
We're not done drinking!

288
00:15:00,500 --> 00:15:02,750
♪Let's make a pair♪

289
00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:04,160
♪On golden sands♪

290
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:07,080
Hello,

291
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:07,790
Sheng Shi.

292
00:15:07,910 --> 00:15:09,250
You finally answered.

293
00:15:09,910 --> 00:15:11,580
Where are you?

294
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:12,750
Is something wrong?

295
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,040
No.

296
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:15,870
I'm sorry. I'll be there soon.

297
00:15:15,950 --> 00:15:17,290
Forget it. Don't bother.

