00:15:17,830 --> 00:15:18,500
I need to go.

299
00:15:18,540 --> 00:15:19,540
Mo...

300
00:15:28,830 --> 00:15:29,700
Mr. Sheng.

301
00:15:29,830 --> 00:15:30,750
Huan.

302
00:15:32,410 --> 00:15:34,250
Make sure everything's ready

303
00:15:34,330 --> 00:15:35,790
for when Lanshan gets home.

304
00:15:35,910 --> 00:15:36,450
Check the lights outside

305
00:15:36,540 --> 00:15:38,120
and in the hallway.

306
00:15:38,290 --> 00:15:39,040
They're on.

307
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:40,540
She's afraid of the dark.

308
00:15:40,910 --> 00:15:42,080
Got it.

309
00:15:42,290 --> 00:15:43,790
Is Lanshan okay?

310
00:15:43,910 --> 00:15:45,660
What could happen to her?

311
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:46,790
Just let me know

312
00:15:46,910 --> 00:15:48,450
when she's back.

313
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:49,250
Alright.

314
00:15:49,330 --> 00:15:50,290
I will.

315
00:15:50,410 --> 00:15:51,500
Shi!

316
00:15:55,160 --> 00:15:57,290
I need to talk to you.

317
00:15:57,410 --> 00:15:59,000
You'll want to hear this.

318
00:16:00,910 --> 00:16:02,160
Sorry, Miss Wang,

319
00:16:02,580 --> 00:16:03,580
but I doubt there's anything about you

320
00:16:03,700 --> 00:16:05,120
that interests me.

321
00:16:05,250 --> 00:16:06,950
It's about Gu Lanshan.

322
00:16:08,330 --> 00:16:09,200
Now,

323
00:16:09,330 --> 00:16:10,620
are you interested?

324
00:16:14,830 --> 00:16:16,120
This is what I wanted to tell you.

325
00:16:16,160 --> 00:16:17,740
Just say it.

326
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:19,410
I'm not in the mood for games.

327
00:16:19,660 --> 00:16:20,200
You might not care now,

328
00:16:20,330 --> 00:16:22,080
but take a look at this.

329
00:16:29,660 --> 00:16:31,580
I happened to see her

330
00:16:31,740 --> 00:16:32,990
buying a tie.

331
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:33,790
Since both your birthday

332
00:16:33,950 --> 00:16:35,660
and Chengchi's are coming up,

333
00:16:35,740 --> 00:16:36,620
I wasn't sure

334
00:16:36,740 --> 00:16:38,540
who it was for, so I took a photo.

335
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:39,990
But today,

336
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:41,830
I saw Chengchi wearing that exact tie.

337
00:16:41,990 --> 00:16:42,990
That means...

338
00:16:46,790 --> 00:16:48,450
What's she been up to

339
00:16:48,580 --> 00:16:50,740
behind your back?

340
00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:54,740
Which mall was this?

341
00:16:54,950 --> 00:16:55,830
Wandu Mall.

342
00:16:56,870 --> 00:16:57,700
Got it.

343
00:16:58,540 --> 00:16:59,410
Shi!

344
00:16:59,660 --> 00:17:01,410
I know you don't like me,

345
00:17:01,490 --> 00:17:02,740
but I have to say,

346
00:17:02,950 --> 00:17:04,540
Lanshan's in love
with her brother-in-law.

347
00:17:04,580 --> 00:17:06,240
Why are you still so good to her?

348
00:17:06,580 --> 00:17:07,790
If this gets out,

349
00:17:07,950 --> 00:17:09,410
how will you save face?

350
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:13,740
I like you, Shi.

351
00:17:14,410 --> 00:17:15,910
I really do.

352
00:17:16,410 --> 00:17:17,200
Even if you never like me back,

353
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:19,330
I don't mind.

354
00:17:31,700 --> 00:17:33,790
It's like they say

355
00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:37,660
that if the fish wants to bite,

356
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:39,450
let it.

357
00:17:39,540 --> 00:17:41,620
As long as she's with me,

358
00:17:42,080 --> 00:17:44,040
I don't care

359
00:17:45,370 --> 00:17:46,830
who she loves.

360
00:18:00,950 --> 00:18:01,740
Here.

361
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,620
This tie really suits you.

362
00:18:05,870 --> 00:18:06,700
Does it?

363
00:18:06,830 --> 00:18:07,950
I really like it.

364
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:13,330
Looks great, right?

365
00:18:17,990 --> 00:18:18,910
Where are you going?

366
00:18:19,080 --> 00:18:20,990
Sneaking away from the drinks?

367
00:18:21,620 --> 00:18:23,200
Come on, let's have another round!

368
00:18:23,660 --> 00:18:24,660
Let's have another one.

369
00:18:25,290 --> 00:18:25,870
Come on.

370
00:18:25,990 --> 00:18:26,490
Shwenny,

371
00:18:26,580 --> 00:18:27,870
- happy birthday.
- Happy birthday.

372
00:18:39,520 --> 00:18:41,640
[Transaction location: LILANZ]

373
00:18:42,290 --> 00:18:44,620
Can't believe she actually bought it.

374
00:19:07,990 --> 00:19:09,450
Ye Chu,

375
00:19:10,040 --> 00:19:11,290
how could you be so heartless?

376
00:19:11,370 --> 00:19:13,200
Why are you doing this to me?

377
00:19:15,410 --> 00:19:17,620
I thought things were getting better

378
00:19:18,870 --> 00:19:20,950
between us.

379
00:19:22,830 --> 00:19:24,700
Was I just imagining it?

380
00:19:27,910 --> 00:19:28,990
Ye Chu,

381
00:19:29,450 --> 00:19:32,200
what am I supposed to do with you?

382
00:19:32,220 --> 00:19:35,850
♪Can't take you running away♪

383
00:19:36,390 --> 00:19:40,180
♪Hurt me all the way♪

384
00:19:40,560 --> 00:19:44,520
♪I'm addicted, no cure♪

385
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:48,520
♪The toughest puzzle I endure♪

386
00:19:48,520 --> 00:19:51,270
♪Our problem was clear♪

387
00:19:52,220 --> 00:19:55,770
♪I lost myself here♪

388
00:19:56,390 --> 00:20:00,140
♪I think of her, no reply♪

389
00:20:00,430 --> 00:20:04,220
♪Scars don't heal, still I try♪

390
00:20:04,430 --> 00:20:07,680
♪I said I wouldn't cry♪

391
00:20:07,770 --> 00:20:11,270
♪Even at the brink♪

392
00:20:12,430 --> 00:20:16,270
♪Missing you, a cruel link♪

393
00:20:17,040 --> 00:20:18,450
Even if I'm a bit late,

394
00:20:18,870 --> 00:20:20,910
there's still time, right?

395
00:20:21,060 --> 00:20:24,180
♪A smile is the classy thing♪

396
00:20:24,310 --> 00:20:30,520
♪I've bet everything♪

397
00:20:39,660 --> 00:20:41,540
Lanshan, you're finally back.

398
00:20:41,660 --> 00:20:43,040
Mr. Sheng couldn't reach you

399
00:20:43,120 --> 00:20:44,040
and was worried sick.

400
00:20:44,120 --> 00:20:46,700
He even called the old house
looking for you.

401
00:20:46,950 --> 00:20:48,490
Sorry for worrying you.

402
00:20:48,660 --> 00:20:50,740
Thank goodness you're back.

403
00:20:50,870 --> 00:20:51,540
That's what matters.

404
00:20:51,660 --> 00:20:52,370
Thanks

405
00:20:52,450 --> 00:20:53,540
for turning on the lights, too.

406
00:20:53,700 --> 00:20:55,490
That was Mr. Sheng's idea.

407
00:20:55,700 --> 00:20:56,950
He knows you're not a fan of the dark

408
00:20:57,120 --> 00:20:58,700
and wanted everything lit up

409
00:20:58,870 --> 00:21:00,490
before you got home.

410
00:21:00,660 --> 00:21:01,370
I see.

411
00:21:01,450 --> 00:21:02,490
You can go rest now.

412
00:21:02,620 --> 00:21:03,080
Alright.

413
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,120
We're leaving now.

414
00:21:04,240 --> 00:21:05,490
You take care, too.

415
00:21:25,620 --> 00:21:26,620
Mrs. Sheng.

416
00:21:27,450 --> 00:21:28,790
How much did you drink?

417
00:21:35,040 --> 00:21:36,200
What are you doing?

418
00:21:36,620 --> 00:21:37,790
My wife's here.

419
00:21:37,950 --> 00:21:38,990
Don't touch me.

420
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:41,240
Don't touch me.

421
00:21:41,990 --> 00:21:43,620
Sorry. He's drunk.

422
00:21:43,870 --> 00:21:45,240
You should head home.

423
00:21:45,450 --> 00:21:46,160
Alright.

424
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:50,910
Come on, let's get you to bed.

425
00:21:53,290 --> 00:21:54,660
What,

426
00:21:54,830 --> 00:21:56,830
feeling rich with my card now?

427
00:21:56,950 --> 00:21:58,660
You used to care when I came home,

428
00:21:58,740 --> 00:22:00,740
no matter what time.

429
00:22:01,870 --> 00:22:03,040
Are you just acting up

430
00:22:03,120 --> 00:22:04,330
because you're drunk?

431
00:22:04,450 --> 00:22:05,950
Ouch, that hurts!

432
00:22:10,450 --> 00:22:11,330
Sit down.

433
00:22:12,790 --> 00:22:13,700
Okay.

434
00:22:19,490 --> 00:22:20,790
I'll grab your shoes.

435
00:22:25,830 --> 00:22:26,660
Change into these.

436
00:22:33,950 --> 00:22:35,080
Sheng Shi!

437
00:22:35,370 --> 00:22:37,740
What are you doing? You're soaked!

438
00:22:37,870 --> 00:22:38,990
Taking a shower.

439
00:22:40,990 --> 00:22:41,990
Don't...

440
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:43,540
The water's still on.

441
00:22:47,490 --> 00:22:48,700
Stop it.

442
00:22:49,290 --> 00:22:50,160
Sheng Shi.

443
00:22:52,450 --> 00:22:53,540
Come here.

444
00:22:53,540 --> 00:22:55,890
♪Reliving sweet times with you♪

445
00:22:56,410 --> 00:22:57,660
Chu,

446
00:22:58,950 --> 00:23:01,330
can I just hold you for a bit?

447
00:23:02,290 --> 00:23:04,410
Just for a moment.

448
00:23:05,290 --> 00:23:06,990
It's all my fault.

449
00:23:07,580 --> 00:23:09,740
I lost you.

450
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:12,950
I can't find you.

451
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,910
How did we

452
00:23:17,040 --> 00:23:19,370
end up like this?

453
00:23:19,700 --> 00:23:20,950
Sheng Shi,

454
00:23:21,990 --> 00:23:23,160
I don't

455
00:23:23,540 --> 00:23:25,160
have feelings for Chengchi,

456
00:23:26,540 --> 00:23:28,120
but I need time

457
00:23:28,370 --> 00:23:30,910
to get over what happened.

458
00:23:32,490 --> 00:23:34,330
Can you give me that?

459
00:23:34,700 --> 00:23:36,870
I'll try to bring back
the Chu you remember,

460
00:23:37,490 --> 00:23:39,540
and you'll bring back
the Shwenny I knew.

461
00:23:42,830 --> 00:23:43,870
Sheng Shi?

462
00:23:45,740 --> 00:23:46,790
Sheng Shi?

463
00:23:47,700 --> 00:23:48,660
Sheng Shi?

464
00:24:02,330 --> 00:24:03,790
Sprouts.

465
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:12,740
Garlic.

466
00:24:16,790 --> 00:24:17,950
Salt.

467
00:24:23,910 --> 00:24:25,370
Too much again.

468
00:24:25,660 --> 00:24:27,540
Lanshan, what are you doing?

469
00:24:27,870 --> 00:24:28,790
Need a hand?

470
00:24:28,870 --> 00:24:29,660
Sheng Shi drank too much.

471
00:24:29,700 --> 00:24:30,740
I'm making him some soup to sober up.

472
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:31,660
I'll do it.

473
00:24:31,700 --> 00:24:33,370
No, it's fine. I got it.

474
00:24:33,620 --> 00:24:35,120
Okay, I'll leave you to it.

475
00:24:47,490 --> 00:24:49,540
Get up and drink this.

476
00:25:07,620 --> 00:25:08,910
I'm sorry

477
00:25:09,580 --> 00:25:12,290
I missed your birthday.

478
00:25:13,870 --> 00:25:14,870
And...

479
00:25:15,830 --> 00:25:17,040
Happy birthday.

480
00:25:45,700 --> 00:25:46,990
What,

481
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:49,040
feeling rich with my card now?

482
00:25:49,160 --> 00:25:50,830
You used to care when I came home,

483
00:25:50,910 --> 00:25:52,830
no matter what time.

484
00:25:54,040 --> 00:25:55,040
Are you just acting up

485
00:25:55,120 --> 00:25:56,580
- because you're drunk?
- Ouch, that hurts!

486
00:25:56,990 --> 00:25:59,040
Did I say something

487
00:25:59,120 --> 00:26:01,450
that made Chu leave?

488
00:26:07,410 --> 00:26:09,120
No more drinking for me.

489
00:26:09,200 --> 00:26:11,490
This mouth of mine...

490
00:26:21,330 --> 00:26:22,540
This tie

491
00:26:22,740 --> 00:26:25,080
is my favorite!

492
00:26:37,490 --> 00:26:38,580
You are awake.

493
00:26:38,870 --> 00:26:39,910
Is your head still hurting?

494
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:44,620
We need to talk.

495
00:26:45,580 --> 00:26:46,990
Think about

496
00:26:47,580 --> 00:26:49,790
who you're living with every day.

497
00:26:50,240 --> 00:26:51,910
What are you talking about?

498
00:26:54,540 --> 00:26:55,080
Sheng Shi.

499
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:56,200
What?

500
00:26:56,950 --> 00:26:57,830
Make it quick.

501
00:26:57,870 --> 00:26:59,370
I'm late for work.

502
00:27:01,080 --> 00:27:02,990
This is your birthday gift.

503
00:27:03,120 --> 00:27:04,700
I didn't know what you'd like,

504
00:27:04,950 --> 00:27:06,950
so I just got something I like.

505
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:08,290
Though I did use your card

506
00:27:08,410 --> 00:27:10,660
to buy it,

507
00:27:10,740 --> 00:27:11,990
I hope you like it.

508
00:27:12,490 --> 00:27:14,330
Take a look.

509
00:27:14,540 --> 00:27:16,120
Maybe I was wrong about her.

510
00:27:16,290 --> 00:27:18,290
Also, it's late,

511
00:27:18,490 --> 00:27:19,910
but

512
00:27:20,490 --> 00:27:21,700
happy birthday.

513
00:27:23,040 --> 00:27:24,870
I'm not happy at all.

514
00:27:25,830 --> 00:27:27,790
You just went out
and bought this, didn't you?

515
00:27:28,370 --> 00:27:30,540
And you used my card?

516
00:27:30,620 --> 00:27:31,660
Where's the thought in that?

517
00:27:31,790 --> 00:27:32,790
It's not like that.

518
00:27:32,950 --> 00:27:35,290
I got a call from the hospital

519
00:27:35,410 --> 00:27:36,700
saying Mo woke up.

520
00:27:36,870 --> 00:27:37,910
I rushed over

521
00:27:38,040 --> 00:27:39,830
and missed your call.

522
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:42,620
Don't be mad.

523
00:27:56,580 --> 00:27:57,620
It's really nice.

524
00:28:08,800 --> 00:28:09,080
Hello,

525
00:28:09,080 --> 00:28:09,870
Dr. Wang?

526
00:28:09,990 --> 00:28:10,870
Sheng Shi.

527
00:28:12,240 --> 00:28:13,740
I heard Ye Mo woke up.

528
00:28:14,120 --> 00:28:15,080
How's he doing?

529
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:15,990
He woke up yesterday.

530
00:28:16,080 --> 00:28:17,540
Still under observation.

531
00:28:17,660 --> 00:28:19,040
It's a miracle.

532
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:21,290
Thank you for everything this past year.

533
00:28:21,410 --> 00:28:22,370
It's nothing.

534
00:28:22,790 --> 00:28:25,080
If you hadn't kept
getting experts involved,

535
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:26,870
he wouldn't have recovered this quickly.

536
00:28:27,080 --> 00:28:27,990
But,

537
00:28:28,580 --> 00:28:30,990
don't tell Lanshan.

538
00:28:31,740 --> 00:28:33,870
I don't want her to stress over it.

539
00:28:34,120 --> 00:28:35,660
I don't get why

540
00:28:35,740 --> 00:28:36,790
you keep doing all this

541
00:28:36,950 --> 00:28:38,370
and hiding it.

542
00:28:39,660 --> 00:28:41,120
Just

543
00:28:41,580 --> 00:28:44,080
a little secret between a couple.

544
00:28:45,700 --> 00:28:46,700
Alright, Uncle Wang.

545
00:28:47,040 --> 00:28:49,120
Thanks for looking after Ye Mo.

546
00:28:49,240 --> 00:28:49,830
No problem.

547
00:28:49,830 --> 00:28:51,120
Thanks, Uncle Wang.

548
00:28:51,240 --> 00:28:52,080
Take care.

549
00:29:02,700 --> 00:29:04,620
If I'd known it was for me,

550
00:29:04,790 --> 00:29:07,160
I wouldn't have drunk so much
for nothing last night.

551
00:29:07,580 --> 00:29:09,120
Got angry for no reason.

552
00:29:11,040 --> 00:29:12,950
Chu's got great taste.

553
00:29:13,120 --> 00:29:15,990
This tie really suits me.

554
00:29:27,060 --> 00:29:27,560
Hello,

555
00:29:27,700 --> 00:29:28,620
Shwenny.

556
00:29:28,620 --> 00:29:29,180
Hello?

557
00:29:29,740 --> 00:29:31,240
Nice of you to call.

558
00:29:32,660 --> 00:29:34,290
I wanted to apologize

559
00:29:34,620 --> 00:29:35,700
for leaving yesterday

560
00:29:35,870 --> 00:29:38,080
without saying anything.

561
00:29:38,490 --> 00:29:39,200
How about

562
00:29:39,370 --> 00:29:41,330
I treat you to dinner soon?

563
00:29:43,700 --> 00:29:45,740
No need to wait. How about today?

564
00:29:45,950 --> 00:29:47,740
I'm right by your office.

565
00:29:47,990 --> 00:29:49,220
You're near my office?

566
00:29:49,220 --> 00:29:49,770
Yeah.

567
00:30:17,620 --> 00:30:22,870
♪Poems often go like this♪

568
00:30:23,330 --> 00:30:28,500
♪That moment felt like fate♪

569
00:30:28,660 --> 00:30:32,160
♪Falling for you♪

570
00:30:32,660 --> 00:30:36,870
♪Like spring breeze warmth♪

571
00:30:40,210 --> 00:30:45,290
♪This sweet dream♪

572
00:30:45,870 --> 00:30:50,460
♪Everything about you clear♪

573
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:53,710
♪Every heartbeat close♪

574
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:57,660
♪Sparks fireworks oh♪

575
00:30:57,910 --> 00:31:00,620
♪I miss you, miss you♪

576
00:31:01,160 --> 00:31:03,370
♪If you need me♪

577
00:31:03,830 --> 00:31:08,960
♪I'll hold you tight♪

578
00:31:09,540 --> 00:31:12,040
♪Engrave this beauty♪

579
00:31:12,410 --> 00:31:15,710
♪In my heart♪

580
00:31:16,250 --> 00:31:18,710
♪Every day from now♪

581
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:20,750
♪In my memories♪

582
00:31:20,910 --> 00:31:23,710
♪Replaying it♪

583
00:31:26,290 --> 00:31:30,040
♪Replaying it♪

584
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:45,620
♪I miss you, miss you♪

585
00:31:46,080 --> 00:31:48,370
♪If you need me♪

586
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:53,960
♪I'll hold you tight♪

